Package de.weltraumschaf.jebnf.gfx.shapes

Railroad shapes package.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Adjustable Implementors can adjust their size and/or position.
Paintable Implementors can paint them selves on a graphics context.
Shape Defines the interface for railroad shapes.
 

Class Summary
AbstractShape Common functionality of shapes.
CompundShapeFactory Creates compound shapes.
ForkShapeFactory Creates fork shapes.
ShapeFactory Factory to create shape objects.
StraightAndCurveShapeFactory Creates straight and curve shapes.
 

Enum Summary
Curves Type of curve railroad shapes.
Straights Type of straight railroad shapes.

Railroad shapes package.
